    "summary": "\"You can't climb the ladder of success with your hands in your pockets!\" - Arnold Schwarzenegger\n\nThe commercial world (and associated leadership) has undergone significant changes in recent years. In what ways do you plan to work on further developing yourself and achieving more commercial success?\n\n\ud835\uddd4\ud835\uddef\ud835\uddfc\ud835\ude02\ud835\ude01 \ud835\udde0\ud835\uddf2 \ud83d\udd0e\nA Brabander at heart, living in Roosendaal, working in Antwerp, 's-Hertogenbosch, Utrecht, and the rest of the Netherlands. A football enthusiast, beginner DJ, gaming guru, lover of meeting interesting people and a fan of making lists.\n\n\ud835\uddd4\ud835\uddef\ud835\uddfc\ud835\ude02\ud835\ude01 \ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf5\ud835\uddf2 \ud835\udddc\ud835\uddfb\ud835\ude00\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\ude01\ud835\ude02\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf2 \ud835\uddf3\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddff \ud835\udde6\ud835\uddee\ud835\uddf9\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude00 \ud835\uddd4\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf1 \ud835\udde0\ud835\uddee\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddf8\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude01\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf4 (\ud835\udddc\ud835\udde6\ud835\uddd4\ud835\udde0) \ud83c\udf93\nThe Institute for Sales And Marketing, ISAM for short, is the Trusted Advisor for shaping, implementing, and empowering commercial transformations within organizations. ISAM's service offerings include four main components:\n\n\ud83d\udd39Postgraduate programs for personal development.\n\ud83d\udd39In-company programs to enhance the performance of individuals and the entire commercial organization.\n\ud83d\udd39Project-based consulting and implementation of commercial policies for the benefit of the commercial organization.\n\ud83d\udd39Professional experts providing advice and hands-on guidance on a consultancy and interim basis.\n\n\ud835\uddd4\ud835\uddf0\ud835\uddf5\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude03\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddfa\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddfb\ud835\ude01\ud835\ude00 \ud83e\udd1d\ud83c\udffc\nSo far, with ISAM's postgraduate education offerings, I have assisted over 200 sales professionals and commercial leaders from more than 100 international companies in their commercial development. If you want to personally develop in the areas of sales, marketing, or leadership, let's get in touch!\n\n\ud83d\udcde +31614814456\n\ud83d\udce7 bas.vanbeek@isam.nl\n\ud83c\udf10 www.isam.nl",
