                    "company": "ISAM | Institute for Sales And Marketing",
                    "description": "The European Institute for Sales, is a well-known postgraduate institute for sales executive education. The courses are based on state-of-the-art knowledge and preparations with a solid scientific basis.\n\nAn external scientific council with 8 highly qualified professors from different universities in Europe is responsible for the level of knowledge and the continuous development of the curriculum. Together with the technical knowledge from the field, they translate the latest scientific knowledge and exercises into account management and sales (management) practice.\n\nThe European Institute for Sales stems from the Institute for Sales and Account Management (ISAM) of Erasmus University Rotterdam. The team has successfully trained more than 6,500 trained leaders and sales professionals since 1996 and is an authority on next-level sales executive education.\n\nEuropean Institute for Sales Education Programs:\n\n\u2666 Strategic Account Management\nThe Strategic Account Management education is aimed at experienced sales professionals who want to develop their knowledge and advanced and who are also looking for the latest (evidence-based) models and methodologies. The program strengthens your knowledge and understanding of markets, organizations and people.\n\n\u2666 Sales Leadership\nThe Sales Leadership education is experienced as sales managers who want to let themselves and their team excel. The education inspires you to look at the environment in which you operate in order to better coach and inspire your team, so that you can add more value to the relationship with customers.\n\n\u2666 Master in Sales\nA unique one-day program of state-of-the-art knowledge from science and next-level developed from the business community, intended for ambitious and sales professionals, (key) account managers, sales managers and commercial executives.",
                    "title": "Account Manager Educations",
                    "employment_type": "Full-time"
                },
                {
